{{en-verb}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[fill]] (something) to excess.
#: {{syn|en|stuff}}
#* {{RQ:Shakespeare Tempest|3|3|text=You are three men of sin, whom Destiny,<br>That hath to instrument this lower world<br>And what is in’t,—the never-'''surfeited''' sea<br>Hath caused to belch up you;}}
