#* '''1795''', {{w|Richard Cumberland (dramatist)|Richard Cumberland}}, ''Henry,'' London: Charles Dilly, Volume{{nbsp}}4, Book{{nbsp}}10, Chapter{{nbsp}}3, p.{{nbsp}}18,<sup>[http://name.umdl.umich.edu/004875941.0001.004]</sup>
